data.description: LOCATION,LOCATION,LOCATION!!.... FULLY PAID OFF SOLAR PANELS Introducing this move-in ready 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home in SERA BELLA COMMUNITY. The mature landscaping,paver driveway, and stone accents on the front of the home invite you to see all that this home has to offer. Upon entering the open-plan living, dining areas are perfectly set up for family sharing and entertainment. The next focal point of this home is the tastefully appointed kitchen with upgraded countertops, backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and a spacious island. Very spacious master bedroom and an ensuite bathroom. The other two bedrooms are generously sized and share a nicely appointed bathroom. Spacious lanai and extensive upscale pavered hardscaping, both with an unobstructed view of the lake. Close to schools, hospitals, shopping, and dining. Nestled between Lake Nona and Kissimmee, you’ll be in close proximity to East Lake Toho, Remington Golf Club, and Medical City. You’ll also have quick access to Orlando International Airport, 417, and Florida’s Turnpike.
